1
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:34,620
It seems you've already recognized each other.

2
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:37,160
What a good show you put on.

3
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:40,640
From pretending to fall into the trap to the final counterattack,

4
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:41,920
brilliant.

5
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,320
It's a pity

6
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:45,280
that it didn't follow my script.

7
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,120
I said

8
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:50,000
I would turn you back into a dead person.

9
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:52,450
Don't you dare hurt him!

10
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:54,880
Su Cheng.

11
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,720
When did you see through me?

12
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,320
In this world,

13
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:13,160
only Gu Chengyu knows I gave that flower a name,

14
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,320
Yuyun Flower,

15
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:18,400
while you called it that yellow flower.

16
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:22,080
I didn't expect my entire plan

17
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:25,039
to be ruined by a yellow flower.

18
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:28,320
You deceived us, used us,

19
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,530
and made both of us change our faces

20
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,690
just for your own selfish desires.

21
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,960
Why didn't you hurt me?

22
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,920
I never wanted to hurt you.

23
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,800
You never wanted to?

24
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,800
Then why did you go to such lengths to make him hurt me?

25
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,600
I just wanted to make you hate him,

26
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,440
resent him,

27
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,240
and be unable to love him.

28
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:59,700
Because he doesn't deserve your love at all.

29
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,200
He doesn't deserve my love.

30
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,960
Do you?

31
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:06,840
Of course.

32
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:10,199
Because I am the real Gu Chengyu.

33
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,280
What do you mean?

34
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,440
I told you,

35
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,600
when the time is right,

36
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,400
I would tell you the whole truth.

37
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,400
It seems that now

38
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,360
is the time.

39
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,360
Nineteen years ago,

40
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,480
my name was Gu Chengyu.

41
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,560
I was a child of a wealthy family.

42
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:39,079
But no one knew I was fostered in the Gu family.

43
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:41,160
The one who left me there was my biological father,

44
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,440
the former emperor.

45
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,160
As the emperor's illegitimate son,

46
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,360
the Gu family should have treated me well.

47
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,840
But not long after,

48
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:51,700
officials usurped the throne and killed my father.

49
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:54,760
We cannot keep this remnant of the previous dynasty.

50
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,760
I agree we should kill him,

51
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,640
lest he implicate us.

52
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,920
Killing innocent people

53
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:59,079
is already wrong.

54
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:01,340
Ending a family line brings worse karma.

55
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,320
Forget it.

56
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,320
Let him stay and fend for himself.

57
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,680
From then on,

58
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:11,800
I went from a prince to an outcast.

59
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,680
I was treated as a servant,

60
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,040
living a life worse than a dog.

61
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,800
At a young age,

62
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,680
I saw through the coldness of the world

63
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,280
and the darkness of human nature.

64
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:26,200
I had nothing left to live for in this world.

65
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,760
Why? No!

66
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,240
Right at that moment,

67
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,360
I met a girl.

68
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,480
It's great to be alive.

69
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,840
Why would you want to die?

70
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:41,200
That girl gave me love and hope.

71
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,400
I also swore to make her

72
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,260
the happiest person in the world.

73
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,960
That girl

74
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,840
is you.

75
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,880
Unfortunately,

76
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,960
I couldn't even protect myself back then.

77
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,960
Until one day,

78
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,860
my opportunity finally came.

79
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,080
Gu Chengyu.

80
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,240
Who are you?

81
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,240
I am your grandfather.

82
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,800
I'm here to take you away,

83
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:21,540
to take back everything that belongs to you,

84
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,040
including this world.

85
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,320
Come out.

86
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:37,040
This is the shadow I carefully selected for you.

87
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,040
From now on,

88
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:42,000
he will take your place and stay in the Gu family.

89
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,880
And you

90
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,840
will become the king above all men

91
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,920
and rule the world.

92
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,360
That's right.

93
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,640
I am that shadow.

94
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:07,960
You are also a liar.

95
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,760
I spent ten years

96
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,220
fighting bloody battles,

97
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,760
monopolizing military power in the name of the God of War.

98
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,880
I only needed financial power to restore the country.

99
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,720
Jiuyun.

100
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,760
Do you know why the God of War must wear a mask?

101
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:33,240
Because my original face...

102
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:36,210
It was destroyed in the flames of war long ago.

103
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,370
I've wondered countless times

104
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:41,560
if you wouldn't recognize me because of this face.

105
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,360
But I don't regret it.

106
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,760
Because without these sacrifices,

107
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,480
I wouldn't be able to fulfill my vow.

108
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,060
I had planned everything perfectly.

109
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,240
Unfortunately, I didn't expect...

110
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,360
Shadow.

111
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:09,600
You actually used my identity to fall in love with the person I love.

112
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,400
Tell me, aren't you a liar?

113
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,920
Jiuyun.

114
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,640
You know the truth now.

115
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,440
Come with me.

116
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,080
Bo Baorui.

117
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,320
Zhong Xiaqiang.

118
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,250
Zhong Xiaqiang.

119
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,170
Peng Yin.

120
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:46,520
Zijian Qiangqipin, Peng Yin.

121
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,560
Zijian Qiangqipin.

122
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,290
Quan Xuhang.

123
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:49,120
Quan Yulong.

124
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:49,850
Quan Yulong.

125
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:50,940
Licheng Lefei.

126
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,300
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing.

127
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:56,080
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo.
